{"type": "article", "id": 12445, "title": "“Fresh Cuts”系列椅子", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-22T07:45:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122508x9BDhjM26OmYoXgn.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t以色列设计师 Ronen Kadushin 推出了一套叫做 “Fresh Cuts” 的系列椅子，其中 “Explicit” 引起了许多人的关注。去年卡戴珊一组翘臀照片红透全世界，女性的臀部似乎在受到前所未有的关注，这个椅子看上去就像一个美女翘着双腿，设计师希望人们借此对这一现象进行思考。另外，这套椅子里面还有展现日本武士精神的 “Samurai”，展现动物困境的 “Wildlife” 等等。所有的椅子的设计都非常简洁，采用 18mm 数控切割胶合板等组建组装而成。而开放式的设计允许所有人直接下载它们。这是<a href=\"http://www.ronen-kadushin.com/\" target=\"_blank\">下载链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140159fZCxbMDIFwQTGYa2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.56601467\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140200d48BkGxPbrmvO17J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.91564792\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140201FQuxObR01Lg92aTY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.65158924\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140201Dvb2rw9iPM415FVe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.88141809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140201OCmtlkR7Vg9w8oTH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8190709\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140202RIc4EQU9StlrJbdF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140202DLeXrzB1oiQk4uUT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7591687\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140203g39ynIovV0XQNCdu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68337408\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}